<p>Jordan Flake has dedicated nearly two decades to helping families in Henderson, Las Vegas, and throughout Nevada plan for the future and protect their legacies. His practice focuses exclusively on estate planning, trust administration, and probate — the areas of law that matter most when families are at their most vulnerable.</p>
<p>A graduate of the University of Michigan Law School, Jordan combines rigorous legal training with a genuine, empathetic approach. He's the attorney who sits with you, listens to your concerns about your family, and then builds a plan that addresses every contingency — not just the obvious ones.</p>
